snippet.title: Jupi Plays Indie Games: ALL THE INDIE GAMES [GBJam 4] [Part 15]
snippet.description:
Basically I wanted to play all of the games that were entered in the GBJam 4, so I did. The theme of this jam was Game Boy Inspired games! You can check out all the games here: http://jams.gamejolt.io/gbjam4/games?sort=oldest
------------------------------------------------
Those Fiends! - http://gamejolt.com/games/those-fiends/85811
Where’s My Dog - http://gamejolt.com/games/where-s-my-dog/87073 
Zom-Boy - http://gamejolt.com/games/zom-boy/87078 
Descend Into Heaven - http://gamejolt.com/games/descend-into-heaven/87079 
Assault on Slime Forestress - http://gamejolt.com/games/assault-on-slime-fortress/87068 
Red and Shark - http://gamejolt.com/games/red-and-shark/87080 
Climbing Hero - http://gamejolt.com/games/climbing-hero/87083 
Trappy Mine - http://gamejolt.com/games/trappy-mine/85941 
Graveyard Garden - http://gamejolt.com/games/graveyard-garden/87085 
Roll FTW - http://gamejolt.com/games/roll-ftw/86770
------------------------------------------------
